column2: SELECT top # objID, ra, dec, (CASE WHEN q.type IS NULL THEN &&& ELSE &&& END) AS found FROM PhotoObj AS p OUTER APPLY dbo.fFootprintEq(ra,dec,#) AS q WHERE (ra BETWEEN # AND #) AND (dec BETWEEN # AND #) SELECT dbo.fInFootprintEq(#, #, #) SELECT dbo.fInFootprintEq(t.ra, t.dec, #) FROM MyTable_# AS t
